quran[7{c,v,t}:
6,95,"danay aur ghuthli ko pharnay wala Allah hai wohi zindah ko murda se nkalta hai aur wohi murda ko zindah se kharij karta hai yeh saaray kaam karne wala Allah hai, phir tum kidhar behke chalay ja rahay ho ?"
6,96,parda shab ko chaak kar ke wohi subah nkalta hai usi ne raat ko sukoon ka waqt banaya hai usi ne chaand aur Sooraj ke tulu o ghuroob ka hisaab muqarrar kya hai yeh sab usi zabardast qudrat aur ilm rakhnay walay ke tehra-ay hue andazay hain
6,97,aur wohi hai jis ne tumahray liye taron ko sehraa aur samandar ki tarikeon mein rasta maloom karne ka zareya banaya dekho hum ne nishanain khol kar bayan kar di hain unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhtay hain
6,98,aur wohi hai jis ne aik mutnaqas se tum ko peed a kya phir har aik ke liye aik jaye qarar hai aur aik is ke sonpe jaane ki jagah yeh nishanain hum ne wazeh kar di hain unn logon ke liye jo samajh boojh rakhtay hain
6,99,"aur wohi hai jis ne aasman se pani barsaya, phir is ke zareya se har qisam ki nabataat ugai, phir is se harey harey khait aur darakht peda kiye, phir un se teh bah teh charrhey hue danay nikalay aur khajoor ke shagoofon se phalon ke guchay ke guchay peda kiye jo boojh ke maaray jhuke parte hain, aur angoor, Zaitoon aur aanar ke baagh lagaye jin ke phal aik dosray se mlitay jaltay bhi hain aur phir unn ke paknay ki kefiyat zara ghhor ki nazar se dekho, inn cheezon mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain"
6,100,"iss par bhi logon ne junoo ko Allah ka shareektehra diya, halaank woh unn ka khaaliq hai, aur be jaane boojhay is ke liye betay aur betiyan tasneef kar den, halaank woh pak aur baala tar hai unn baton se jo yeh log kehte hain"
6,101,woh to asmano aur zameen ka mo-jad hai is ka koi beta kaisay ho sakta hai jabkay koi is ki shareek zindagi hi nahi hai is ne har cheez ko peda kya hai aur woh har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
